{"word":"G1097 - γινώσκω - ginṓskō - ghin-oce'-ko - Allow","slug":"G1097","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">γινώσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ginṓskō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ghin-oce'-ko"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Allow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B3;&#x03B9;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03C9; - gino&#x0304;sko&#x0304;</b> - <i>ghin-oce'-ko</i><p/>A prolonged form of a primary verb; to &ldquo;know&rdquo; (absolutely), in a great variety of applications and with many implications (as shown at left, with others not thus clearly expressed): - allow, be aware (of), feel, (have) known (-ledge), perceive, be resolved, can speak, be sure, understand."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1106\">G1106</a>, <a href=\"#/G1107\">G1107</a>, <a href=\"#/G1108\">G1108</a>, <a href=\"#/G1110\">G1110</a>, <a href=\"#/G176\">G176</a>, <a href=\"#/G1921\">G1921</a>, <a href=\"#/G1922\">G1922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2607\">G2607</a>, <a href=\"#/G4267\">G4267</a>, <a href=\"#/G4268\">G4268</a>, <a href=\"#/G4774\">G4774</a>"}]}